@startuml seq_07_follow_unfollow_user
title Sequence Diagram: UC-07 Follow / Unfollow User

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Follow Controller" as Controller
participant "Follow Service" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Click Follow / Unfollow button
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/users/{target_id}/follow (or DELETE)
Controller -> Service: Toggle Follow Status (followerID, targetID)
Service -> Repo: Check target user exists
Repo --> Service: User exists

alt Action is Follow
    Service -> Repo: Create Follow Relationship
    Repo --> Service: Relationship created
    Service -> Repo: Increment Follower Count
else Action is Unfollow
    Service -> Repo: Remove Follow Relationship
    Repo --> Service: Relationship removed
    Service -> Repo: Decrement Follower Count
end

Service --> Controller: Updated Follow Status
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Update UI button state
@enduml